@startuml
autonumber

actor User

participant "Ordering Service\n(8085)" as Ordering
participant "Payment Service\n(8086)" as Payment
participant "Shipping Service\n(8087)" as Shipping
participant "Order Tracking Service\n(8084)" as Tracking

== Размещение заказа ==
User -> Ordering: POST http://localhost:8085/orders
note right
Создание заказа:
- customerId = 1
- items = [
  { productId: 1, cost: 2000, qty: 1 },
  { productId: 2, cost: 1500, qty: 2 }
]
Возвращает orderId
end note
Ordering -> User: { "id": 1, "status": "PLACED" }

== Подтверждение заказа ==
User -> Ordering: [[http://localhost:8085/orders/1/verification PUT /orders/verification]]
note right
Подтверждение заказа:
- orderId = 1
Меняет статус заказа на CONFIRMED
end note
Ordering -> User: { "id": 1, "status": "CONFIRMED" }

== Оплата заказа ==
User -> Payment: [[http://localhost:8086/payments/byOrder/1 POST /payments]]
note right
Оплата заказа:
- orderId = 1
Запускает процесс оплаты
end note
Payment -> User: "paymentId": 2

User -> Payment: [[http://localhost:8086/payments/byOrder/1/status GET /payments/status]]
note right
Статус платежа:
- orderId = 1
Сначала "IN_PROCESS", затем "PAID"
end note
Payment -> User: "IN_PROCESS"

...Ждём 30 секунд...

User -> Payment: [[http://localhost:8086/payments/byOrder/1/status GET /payments/status]]
Payment -> User: "PAID"

== Автоматический запуск доставки ==
Ordering -> Shipping: [[http://localhost:8087/shipping/1 PUT /shipping]]
note right
Так как заказ оплачен, доставка запускается автоматически
(уже реализовано в задании 2).
Возвращает deliveryId - идентификатор доставки.
end note
Shipping -> Ordering: "deliveryId": 3

User -> Shipping: [[http://localhost:8087/shipping/1/status GET /shipping/{{shippingId}}/status]]
Shipping -> User: "IN_DELIVERY"

== Отслеживание состояния заказа ==
User -> Tracking: [[http://localhost:8084/1 GET http://localhost:8084/{{orderId}}]]
note right
Запрос статуса заказа:
- orderId = 1
Возвращает статусы заказа, оплаты и доставки
end note
Tracking -> Ordering: Запрос статуса заказа
Ordering -> Tracking: { "status": "CONFIRMED" }
Tracking -> Payment: Запрос статуса оплаты
Payment -> Tracking: { "status": "PAID" }
Tracking -> Shipping: Запрос статуса доставки
Shipping -> Tracking: { "status": "IN_DELIVERY" }
Tracking -> User: { "orderStatus": "CONFIRMED", "paymentStatus": "PAID", "shippingStatus": "IN_DELIVERY" }

== Отмена доставки (Trigger Refund) ==
User -> Shipping: [[http://localhost:8087/shipping/1 DELETE /shipping/{{orderId}}]]
note right
Отмена доставки:
- orderId = 1
Запускает процесс возврата денег (refund)
end note
Shipping -> User: "CANCELLED"

== Компенсация: возврат денег ==
Shipping -> Payment: [[http://localhost:8086/payments/refund/1 POST /refund]]
note right
Автоматический возврат платежа:
- orderId = 1
Платёж возвращается
end note
Payment -> User: "REFUNDED"

== Логирование в PaymentService ==
Payment -> Log: "Payment refunded for orderId=1"

@enduml